Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:01.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得那些傢伙會不會來醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一臉不相信的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會信才怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 他們一定會來襲擊人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:15.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼就能這樣斷言？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 就之前的病例來看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不會一下子殺死犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:25.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠在8月12日因貧血倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後病情逐漸惡化 15日死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之間隔了4天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:34.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 可以認為她被吸了4次血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4次？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:40.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說 人如果失去超過50%的循環血液量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會導致心臟停止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:46.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設血液量共4升 那就是2升
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:52.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙大概一次也吸不了2升血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們喝不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:58.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說他們的飯量只有這麼2杯左右
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:03.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設 1次的吸血量是這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2次襲擊就會引起休克症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第4次就會造成心臟停止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:12.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 實際上應該沒有這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 被吸血的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便睡著了也會被驚醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼犧牲者什麼都不說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:22.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說不說 不如說是被什麼禁言了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:23.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像某種昆蟲一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:30.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好會在吸血時 注入類似麻藥的物質
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:34.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 那些傢伙就能操縱犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:40.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:46.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病情穩定了 至少沒有惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 小律 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:53.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是節子婆婆的早飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:56.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然她沒有要吃的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過生命體征已經穩定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她住院應該是做對了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:07.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安代小姐 我們不值夜班真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:10.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧 醫生都說不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:19.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出診工作上午有2個 下午…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:29.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:32.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 下午有1個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:35.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生 節子婆婆怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:37.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問病情嗎 還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這些 今天也拜託各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:45.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節子婆婆的具體治療方案 定下了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒沒有 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:53.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還問怎麼了 大家都很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:56.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生一個人值夜班也太勉強了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不讓我們幫忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那您的意思呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:11.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:14.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方案決定後 會請你們幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:16.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:22.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安代小姐 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來真的很累嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:36.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭子 你怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:39.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被母親叫來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:43.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說是你讓我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:45.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:49.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我為工作奔忙 感到疲憊不堪」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:52.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「既然是我老婆 這種時候就該待在家裡」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:54.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「把店關了給我回來」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:57.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我馬上就知道她是騙我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:08:01.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回去就回去吧 反正你不在也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:03.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你在家我也沒空陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:08.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回什麼啊 我都在店裡貼了暫時關店的通知了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:13.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 看媽媽的心情轉好 你就挑時機回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不說我也會那麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:18.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不能讓你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:23.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭子 你好歹也是尾崎家的兒媳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:27.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫為工作奔忙 你卻想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做人要知廉恥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失言了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:36.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒想到母親您會躲在一旁偷聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:41.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫 你怎麼就這麼忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子裡發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:49.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷有人死亡 不會是傳染病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:52.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:57.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 看起來像是傳染病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:08:58.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:04.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽好了 以後再有那種患者就叫救護車送到別的醫院去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:08.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒必要做危險的事 好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:09.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好什麼好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:15.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫 你是歷史悠久的尾崎家的獨苗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:18.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一你有個好歹 醫院怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:20.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為某人總不回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:22.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連個繼承家業的人都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:23.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:27.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬不得已的話 從親戚中收養個能幹的孩子就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:31.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然 媽媽再婚怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出診去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:39.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還露著大腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:40.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:42.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊 死老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴 給我有教養一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被偷聽的老太婆這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:47.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能偷吃哦 綠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:58.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生他在醫院留宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:03.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為工務店的節子婆婆住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我給他做些慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節子婆婆也病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:10.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家人怎麼了啊 一個接一個的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是姐姐還真是勤快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那位年輕夫人來做不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:18.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回來了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我看到那個人的車了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:23.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭子小姐不是會做這種事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那老太太呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:29.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少住持在陪醫生留宿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:32.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老太太討厭那間寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為比尾崎家還有聲望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:43.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎 你也要去散步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 算了 我一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:03.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:13.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙擁有多大的能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會能變成蝙蝠 還會穿牆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:25.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在電影裡 想擊退他們就得用十字架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:28.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們怕十字架和大蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:31.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鏡子裡照不出來 害怕陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:36.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們對吸血鬼的認識 都是編造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:41.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在這個村子裡有一群吸血殺人的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:20.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:29.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙 只要抓住其中一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:30.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能快點找到辦法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:33.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能進行解剖什麼的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:35.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解剖？等下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:38.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的有吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:43.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了要吸血 別的都和生前沒什麼兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜信 這裡是二樓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:12:59.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:01.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這扇窗的外面…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:05.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有可供踩踏的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:31.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:46.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不允許你隨便進入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:52.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節子婆婆 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:02.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天由我做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:04.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:06.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 小律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起昨天 今天您的心情似乎也好了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:10.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:15.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住院後第3天 節子婆婆的意識變得清醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不適的狀況也改善了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:20.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會成為康復的首例
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:24.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚睡得非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 深夜時有醒來過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:32.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢話也說得相當清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為有誰在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:38.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 夢話什麼的真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說起來 也許是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒回來的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下段日子是奈緒的四十九日了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}四十九日：日本的一種法事 死後每7天一次直至輪至49日\N此法事對死者前往極樂淨土有重要意義
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:50.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是我太在意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:55.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想起來 可能是前天吧 也可能更早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:59.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段時間 一直清晰地做著這種夢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:03.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:10.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那該不會是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:13.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:19.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果奈緒能回來的話 那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有進 幹康也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:22.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節子婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:27.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:33.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你活著沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要吃紅豆餡麵包？來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悶死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:49.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有工作到快死的男人和刁蠻婆婆 我真是嫁錯了人家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:54.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃紅豆餡麵包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:16:00.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫君 少住持 我差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:01.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:04.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節子的狀況好轉了 我也安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:06.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:07.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:09.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:14.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好睡 儘量早點康復吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:17.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就只剩下對方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於睡熟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:37.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙施的催眠術應該也失效了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:39.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:42.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得奈緒今天也會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當她會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:48.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此 如果能知道那些傢伙的弱點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:52.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 吸血鬼的傳說中有這麼一說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:55.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼的話 如果不被邀請 就不能進入人類的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:59.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 如果不說「來我家玩吧」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:02.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就進不了人類的家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:06.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果邀請了 那房子就會對吸血鬼開放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天奈緒沒有進來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:13.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這樣的話就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:15.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停電？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:20.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 村裡的燈火沒有滅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:21.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:24.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能他們的夜視能力比較強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗對我們不利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:28.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得一樓好像有舊發電機來著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:29.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去開啟它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:31.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 靜信 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:33.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:34.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:38.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候不是經常在醫院裡玩探險遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:01.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:05.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到嗎 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到外面來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:09.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節子婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:14.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要去 奈緒在叫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:20.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:34.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:48.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不進來襲擊我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:53.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去的話就會被殺了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:19:00.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們 是進不來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:04.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節子婆婆 快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:08.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以進來哦 只要有人邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:23.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 尾崎醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:28.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節子婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫辰巳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:37.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫 發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:40.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會殺你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:46.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為吩咐過了 我還不能對醫生下手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:53.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節…節子婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:01.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:06.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:10.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節子婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:39.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那些屍變者打算今天一口氣解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:43.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們知道我們藏起了節子婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以速戰速決以免夜長夢多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:48.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了要救她的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:51.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:20:59.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:01.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:04.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:07.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能先回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:08.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:29.72,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}大きな夢 目指し歩いていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:29.72,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}向著遠大的夢想前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:40.23,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}迷い迷って 終わりのない旅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:40.23,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充滿迷惑的無盡的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:52.00,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あの時は雪まじりの雨で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:52.00,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那時候雨雪交織
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:58.05,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}涙かどうか分からなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:58.05,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}落下的是不是眼淚無從知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:05.99,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}さよなら もう二度と会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:05.99,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永別了 已經不會再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:12.42,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私が選んだミライヘ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:12.42,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}朝向我選擇的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:18.11,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}また一歩踏み出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:18.11,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}又向前踏出了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:23.72,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}大きな 壁を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:23.72,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}跨過高大的牆壁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:29.39,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好きだったのにどうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:29.39,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}明明是喜歡的 但為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:34.83,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「最期だ」なんて言ったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:34.83,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要說「最後」兩個字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:39.85,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今ではちゃんと分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:39.85,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如今我完全理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:42.87,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:42.87,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:48.84,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ねぇ "Walk" 強く…
